PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784308721
OL,3,CTribute to mum and two children shot
OL,4,Cdead by Ian Rutledge at Co Fermanagh
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FA priest has told how the grief he saw
OL,8,Fin the families of the Maguiresbridge
OL,9,Fmurder victims would "stay with me for
OL,10,Fever".
OL,12,FHe was speaking ahead of the first
OL,13,Fanniversary of the atrocity in Co
OL,14,FFermanagh in which Ian Ruthledge shot
OL,15,Fdead his partner Vanessa Whyte, 45,
OL,16,Fand his children James , 14, and Sara,
OL,17,F13, before turning the gun on himself.
OL,18,FThe 43-year-old died from his injuries
OL,19,Fdays later.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784308721
OL,3,CTribute to mum and two children shot
OL,4,Cdead by Ian Rutledge at Co Fermanagh
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FFr Raymond Donnelly, of St Michael's
OL,8,FParish, said: "I will never forget the
OL,9,Fvision of the three coffins before me
OL,10,Fin a church. I will never forget the
OL,11,Fgrief on the faces of those families.
OL,12,FIt will stay with me for ever.
OL,14,F"There are two families and we must
OL,15,Freach out to the two families, offer
OL,16,Fthem our prayerful support and our
OL,17,Fdeepest sympathy at all times.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784308721
OL,3,CTribute to mum and two children shot
OL,4,Cdead by Ian Rutledge at Co Fermanagh
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"Grief doesn't disappear after 12
OL,8,Fmonths. It's important to recognize
OL,9,Fthat fact people live with the grief
OL,10,Fof what happened in Maguiresbridge,
OL,11,Fthe loss, tragic loss of life. And the
OL,12,Fone thing I can say is that people did
OL,13,Fcome together at that time, as shocked
OL,14,Fas they were."
OL,16,FAnd Kerrie Flood of Fermanagh and
OL,17,FOmagh Women's Aid said the suspected
OL,18,Fdouble murder and suicide in Ballymena
OL,19,Fon Monday would retraumatise people in
OL,20,Fthe community.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784308721
OL,3,CTribute to mum and two children shot
OL,4,Cdead by Ian Rutledge at Co Fermanagh
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FShe added: "We know that when this
OL,8,Fhappens again, it brings the trauma
OL,9,Fright back for every family who's been
OL,10,Fthrough it. So that trauma is alive in
OL,11,Four communities, and it's alive in our
OL,12,Ffamilies."
OL,14,FA vigil was held in Ballymena on
OL,15,FWednesday night in honour of the
OL,16,Ftragic mum and daughter who were
OL,17,Fkilled. The pair - a woman of 39 and a
OL,18,Fgirl aged eight - were found dead
OL,19,Falong with a man of 41 in a house in
OL,20,Fthe Cullybackey Road area of the town
OL,21,Fon Monday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784308721
OL,3,CTribute to mum and two children shot
OL,4,Cdead by Ian Rutledge at Co Fermanagh
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FMid & East Antrim District Commander,
OL,8,FSuperintendent William Calderwood
OL,9,Fsaid: "Our officers attended with
OL,10,Fcolleagues from the Northern Ireland
OL,11,FAmbulance Service where they were met
OL,12,Fwith a shocking scene.
OL,14,F"Tragically, the bodies of three
OL,15,Fpeople from the same family...were
OL,16,Flocated in the home.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784308721
OL,3,CTribute to mum and two children shot
OL,4,Cdead by Ian Rutledge at Co Fermanagh
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"A strong hypothesis is that this was
OL,8,Fa double murder followed by a sudden
OL,9,Fdeath. As such, at this stage, we are
OL,10,Fnot looking for anybody else in
OL,11,Fconnection with the deaths."
OL,13,FThe vigil was organised by Ballymena-
OL,14,Fbased Youth Ambassadors Northern
OL,15,FIreland. They said prior to the event:
OL,16,F"We will remember the innocent lives
OL,17,Flost, support everyone affected, and
OL,18,Fstand together as one community. Our
OL,19,Fthoughts are with the family, friends,
OL,20,Fneighbours and the Polish community
OL,21,Fduring this incredibly difficult time."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
